                      votes <span class="ItemCaption">Reviewed: </span>
                      <span>2003-05-13</span>
                    </div>
                    <span>If you are looking to gain a better understanding of salary economics related to baseball, search no further. The Money Pitch is a good resource to educate any reader about the principles and logic behind such a huge economic enterprise. This book is very informative and reveals many facts that are not common knowledge. Upon reading this book one gains a new perspective toward baseball and broadens his understanding of how economics are applied in sports.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Don't be a hater Roger jus cause you ain't makin big bucks</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
                      <span>3</span>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Helpful: </span>
                      <span>1</span>
                      /
